Class Meal

java.lang.Object
Food.MenuItem
Food.Meal
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
FullMeal, HalfMeal
public abstract class Meal extends MenuItem
Represents a meal, which may include a main dish and additional items.
